An HTTP/1.0 endpoint that always responds with a body that echoes the
requested path (e.g. "checked: /api/users") but whose status varies with
the request method: 200 for GET (read access), 405 for everything else
(method not allowed). This pairs slice 3d (body computed via concat) with
slice 3e (status computed via if/else) inside a single HttpResponse
record — no record duplication.
